    "<b>Procedure:</b><br/>                 If work has been done on the hydraulic unit                  <a class=\"qv qv-grafik\" href=\"\" target=\"PIWIS479cf1285e4a1004848bf59204062835\">-D-</a>                 , the speed sensors and the wire harness or if the hydraulic unit                  <a class=\"qv qv-grafik\" href=\"\" target=\"PIWIS479cf1285e4a1004848bf59204062835\">-D-</a>                  is replaced, an ABS/PSM test (system check) must be performed using the PIWIS Tester! This is the case, for example, after accident repairs! This prevents any confusion of electrical or hydraulic lines and ensures faultless operation of the system!             "
    
